      \\ rw [] \\ res_tac \\ fs [] \\ res_tac \\ fs [])
    \\ Cases_on `max_depth s.stack_size (call_graph funs n ns (size funs2) c1) = NONE`
    THEN1 fs [OPTION_MAP2_DEF] \\ simp []
    \\ Cases_on `s0.stack_size = s.stack_size` \\ fs []
